CEOs%20flying%20to%20candidates%20to%20close%20offers%2C%20significantly%20above-average%20sign-on%20and%20performance%20bonuses%2C%20new%20equity%20structures%2C%20customized%20benefits%20for%20individuals%2C%20and%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Xu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIffi%20Wahla%2C%20CEO%20of%20global%20talent%20network%20Edge%2C%20said%20data%20scientists%20have%20been%20among%20the%20best-paid%20tech%20workers%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20partly%20because%20every%20business%20needs%20people%20who%20can%20understand%20and%20extract%20value%20from%20data.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ECompanies%20want%20to%20spread%20AI%20skills%20across%20their%20operations%2C%20so%20those%20with%20a%20background%20or%20training%20in%20techniques%20such%20as%20prompt%20engineering%20on%20generative%20AI%20will%20benefit%20from%20increased%20job%20opportunities%20and%20pay%2C%20Wahla%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20most%20sought-after%20skills%20that%20may%20help%20you%20land%20a%20well-paying%20job%20in%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAswini%20Thota%2C%20director%20of%20data%20science%20at%20financial%20service%20firm%20USAA%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20when%20hiring%20data%20scientists%20and%20AI%20engineers%2C%20he%20assesses%20candidates%20based%20on%20three%20key%20areas%3A%20technical%20prowess%2C%20business%20acumen%20and%20communication%2C%20and%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22770d000b-61e3-47fa-a646-e4f931dcf6d9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETechnical%20knowledge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThota%20says%20data%20scientists%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20well-versed%20in%20Python%20and%20R%2C%20the%20most%20popular%20programming%20languages%20for%20building%20AI%20models%2C%20while%20some%20companies%20use%20C%2B%2B%20and%20Java.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20also%20expected%20to%20have%20a%20foundational%20knowledge%20of%20statistics%2C%20as%20well%20as%20machine%20learning%20algorithms%20and%20frameworks%20in%20Python%20or%20R.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20vast%20majority%20of%20organizations%20rely%20on%20cloud%20technology%20to%20store%2C%20analyze%2C%20and%20build%20models%2C%20so%20a%20working%20knowledge%20of%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%2C%20Google%20Cloud%20Platform%2C%20Snowflake%2C%20Microsoft%20Azure%2C%20Databricks%2C%20and%20similar%20platforms%20has%20become%20increasingly%20important%20in%20recent%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Thota%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220d17a6e8-d8a6-4e00-957f-f7a31c70048b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBusiness%20acumen%20and%20communication%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Thota%2C%20data%20scientists%20looking%20to%20land%20a%20job%20in%20AI%20should%20also%20have%20strong%20business%20acumen%20to%20grasp%20an%20organization's%20challenges%20and%20develop%20solutions.%20%26quot%3BCommunication%20skills%20come%20into%20play%20when%20data%20scientists%20must%20explain%20the%20results%20and%20influence%20decision-makers%20to%20align%20with%20the%20technical%20approach%20they%20recommend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eaab06a2-f711-40dd-9495-5179cf962dca%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInnovation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20recruiting%20for%20senior%20or%20lead%20roles%2C%20Thota%20says%20he%20looks%20for%20candidates%20who%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20lead%20with%20innovation.%20%26quot%3BHiring%20candidates%20with%20an%20innovative%20mindset%20helps%20us%20anticipate%20and%20address%20potential%20challenges%20before%20they%20become%20issues%20and%20also%20develop%20groundbreaking%20solutions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2213a2fd6f-271b-4dd7-863c-368cb3f48cfb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlexibility%20and%20ongoing%20learning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERam%20Srinivasan%2C%20a%20future%20of%20work%20leader%20at%20consulting%20firm%20JLL%2C%20says%20some%20of%20the%20most%20sought-after%20AI%20competencies%20include%20a%20combination%20of%20technical%20and%20soft%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20include%20having%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20learning%20mindset%2