-pandemic%20that%20require%20getting%20dressed%20up%2C%20which%20is%20when%20I'd%20typically%20wear%20jewelry.%20And%20if%20I%20am%20going%20to%20spend%20time%20on%20my%20appearance%2C%20nine%20times%20out%20of%2010%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20at%20the%20gym%20because%20that's%20where%20I%20get%20the%20benefits%20of%20health%20and%20fitness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhusband-wife-dont-wear-wedding-rings-dont-like-jewlery-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720180562000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664b7f7d20abc1efe8fb9b57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhusband-wife-dont-wear-wedding-rings-dont-like-jewlery-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20husband%20proposed%20with%20a%20ring%2C%20but%20when%20it%20came%20to%20getting%20married%20we%20didn't%20get%20rings%20for%20each%20other.%20People%20find%20it%20weird%2C%20but%20we%20love%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Tracee%20M.%20Herbaugh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhusband-wife-dont-wear-wedding-rings-dont-like-jewlery-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%20Suspends%2016%20Engineers%20After%2010%20Bridges%20Fall%20In%20Quick%20Succession%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESixteen%20engineers%20of%20the%20water%20resources%20department%20in%20Bihar%20have%20been%20suspended%20after%2010%20bridges%20collapsed%20in%20the%20last%2015%20days%20across%20the%20state%2C%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20department%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20Development%20Secretary%20Chaitanya%20Prasad%20told%20reporters%20the%20state%20government%20is%20serious%20about%20the%20issue.%20He%20said%20the%20contractors%20responsible%20for%20building%20the%20bridges%20will%20be%20traced%20and%20