folio%20for%20over%2015%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20RJD%20leader%20%5BTejashwi%20Yadav%5D%20must%20remember%20that%20he%20held%20the%20portfolio%20for%20more%20than%2015%20months%20during%20the%20previous%20mahagathbandhan%20government.%20What%20was%20he%20doing%20then%3F%20The%20previous%20RJD-led%20Bihar%20government%20and%20he%20should%20be%20held%20responsible%20for%20this%20mess%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Choudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720180560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fiko3i118_bihar-bridge-collapse_625x300_04_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbihar-suspends-11-engineers-after-10-bridges-fall-in-quick-succession-6040435%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sixteen%20engineers%20of%20the%20water%20resources%20department%20in%20Bihar%20have%20been%20suspended%20after%2010%20bridges%20collapsed%20in%20the%20last%2015%20days%20across%20the%20state%2C%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20department%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A326%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbihar-suspends-11-engineers-after-10-bridges-fall-in-quick-succession-6040435%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbihar-suspends-11-engineers-after-10-bridges-fall-in-quick-succession-6040435%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbihar-suspends-11-engineers-after-10-bridges-fall-in-quick-succession-6040435%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IEX%20board%20reappoints%20SN%20Goel%20as%20CMD%2C%20promotes%20Rohit%20Bajaj%20as%20Joint%20MD%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720180088000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2015-10%2F14%2Fthumb%2F%2F400X400%2F1444839236-678.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fiex-board-rea