ty's%20ambitious%20call%20to%20secure%20an%20unprecedented%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3E400%20paar%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20%5Bmore%20than%20400%20seats%5D%20majority%20in%20the%20Parliament%20-%20a%20majority%20that%20the%20Opposition%20alleged%20would%20have%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhad-mandate-to-change-constitution-in-last-10-years-but-amit-shah-5681638%5C%22%3Eamending%20the%20Constitution%20easier%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20ruling%20alliance.%20Opposition%20leaders%20even%20declared%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20Constitution%20as%20they%20sloganeered%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Esamvidhan%20khatre%20mein%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20%5Bthe%20Constitution%20is%20in%20danger%5D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20electoral%20outcome%20has%20gone%20on%20to%20make%20the%20pocketbook%20Constitution%20a%20common%20site%20in%20India's%20Parliamentary%20democracy.%20The%20core%20messaging%20of%20this%20optics%20is%20to%20uphold%20the%20protection%20of%20minorities%20and%20caste-based%20affirmative%20action%20%2Freservations%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20To%20Maintain%20Democracy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20famous%201949%20speech%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fbr-ambedkar%5C%22%3EDr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Drafting%20Committee%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20posed%20the%20question%3A%20If%20we%20wish%20to%20maintain%20democracy%20not%20merely%20in%20form%2C%20but%20also%20in%20fact%2C%20what%20must%20we%20do%3F%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20politics%2C%20%3Cem%3EBhakti%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20hero-worship%20is%20a%20sure%20road%20to%20degradation%20and%20to%20eventual%20dictatorship.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ambedkar%20also%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20must%20not%20be%20content%20with%20mere%20political%20democracy.%26quot%3B%20He%20predicted%20that%20an%20emerging%20India%20of%20the%20time%20would%20have%20political%20equality%20(that%20is%2C%20universal%20adult%20franchise%2C%20one-person-one-vote)%2C%20but%20deep%20and%20pervasive%20social%20inequality%20(that%20is%2C%20some%20people's%20lives%20would%20be%20more%20valuable%20than%20the%20others').%20Dr%20Ambedkar%20famously%20called%20this%20%26quot%3Ba%20life%20of%20contradictions%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EResolving%20A%20Life%20Of%20Contradictions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20life%20of%20contradictions%20has%20endured%20for%20over%20seven%20decades%2C%20and%20it%20calls%20for%20a%20deep%20reflection%20on%20our%20societal%20and%20political%20structures.%20In%20his%201949%20speech%2C%20Dr%20Ambedkar%20spoke%20about%20resolving%20the%20contradiction.%20How%20can%20an%20impending%20life%20of%20contradictions%20be%20averted%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20make%20our%20political%20democracy%20a%20social%20democracy%20as%20well.%20Political%20democracy%20cannot%20last%20unless%20there%20lies%20at%20the%20base%20of%20it%20social%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20does%20social%20democracy%20mean%3F%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20posed%20this%20question%20in%20that%20speech%2C%20and%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20means%20a%20way%20of%20life%20which%20recognises%20liberty%2C%20equality%20and%20fraternity%20as%20the%20principles%20of%20life.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fexplained-can-the-indian-constitution-be-changed-784999%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20%7C%C2%A0Explained%3A%20Can%20The%20Indian%20Constitution%20Be%20Changed%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20does%20fraternity%20mean%3F%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Ambedkar%20asked%20himself%2C%20and%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20principle%20which%20gives%20unity%20and%20solidarity%20to%20social%20life.%20%5B...%5D%20In%20India%20there%20are%20castes.%20The%20castes%20are%20anti-national.%20In%20the%20first%20place%20because%20they%20bring%20about%20separation%20in%20social%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20And%20Constitution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaste%20is%20a%20fundamental%20unit%20of%20inequality%20in%20India.%20It%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20site%20of%20Constitutional%20remediation.%20The%20pre-election%20rhetoric%20of%20a%20%26quot%3BConstitution-under-threat%26quot%3B%20perhaps%20delivered%20its%20message%20most%20effectively%20to%20Dalit%2C%20Adivasi%2C%20and%20Bahujan%20voters%2C%20who%20are%20directly%20affected%20by%20caste-based%20inequalities.%20The%20optics%20of%20the%20pocketbook%20Constitution%20have%20outlasted%20electoral%20campaigning%20by%20now.%20Many%20politicians%20are%20seen%20with%20this%20pocketbook%20in%20their%20hands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20gimmick.%20It's%20intended%20to%20attract%20attention.%20The%20Constitution%20of%20India%20is%20famously%20lengthy%3B%20it%20is%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20one%20of%20the%20longest-written%20constitutions%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20optics%20of%20a%20pocketbook%20Constitution%20in%20anyone's%20hands%20does%20not%20imply%20they%20have%20read%20it%20or%20are%20interested%20in%20wading%20through%20this%20lengthy%20text.%20Yet%2C%20the%20optics%20have%20given%20an%20unprecedented%20tangible%20form%20to%20the%20Constitution.%20It%20has%20popularised%20the%20ideas%20of%20Constitutionalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20What%20Is%20Constitutionalism%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20practice%20of%20establishing%2C%20adhering%20to%2C%20and%20respecting%20a%20system%20of%20constitutional%20governance.%20It's%20an%20abstract%20idea%20that%20affects%20everyone%20and%20rarely%20presents%20itself%20in%20tangible%20form%20-%20in%20popular%20cultures%20and%20imaginations.%20Movies%20like%20%3Cem%3EArticle%2015%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2019)%20have%20generated%20the%20optics%2C%20amplified%20the%20text%20of%20Article%2015%2C%20and%20popularised%20the%20idea%20of%20non-discrimination.%20The%20iconography%20of%20Dr.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20with%20the%20Constitution%20in%20his%20hand%20-%20a%20larger-sized%20book%20-%20is%20also%20common%20in%20Dalit%20sub-cultures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F5bo1chto_constitution-poster_625x300_05_July_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrinted%20copies%20of%20this%20poster%20(16%26quot%3Bx%2012%26quot%3B)%20are%20commonly%20sold%20at%20roadside%20stalls%20in%20India%2C%20especially%20on%20Ambedkar%20Jayanti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20nothing%20to%20begrudge%20the%20optics.%20However%2C%20it%20has%20become%20a%20sore%20point%20among%20the%20ruling%20political%20parties%20in%20the%20Parliament%20of%20India%20because%20of%20perhaps%20the%20implied%20perception%20that%20they%20are%20anti-constitutional%20somehow.%20The%20remark%20of%20the%20Speaker%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20at%20Shashi%20Tharoor's%20salutation%20to%20the%20Constitution%20(%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EJai%20Samvidhan%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B)%20is%20perhaps%20an%20example%20of%20this%20political%20soreness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20optics%2C%20nonetheless%2C%20are%20good%20for%20spreading%20aspirational%20ideals%20of%20constitutionalism%20in%20popular%20cultures%20and%20imaginations.%20Even%20if%20it%20is%20momentary%20and%20the%20politicians%20discard%20the%20ideals%20when%20they%20do%20not%20favour%20them%2C%20this%20moment%20will%20endure%20in%20the%20collective%20memories%20and%20consciousness%20of%20a%20rising%20social%20democracy%20in%20India.%20Jai%20Samvidhan.%20Jai%20Bhim.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Prof.%20Dr.%20Sumit%20Baudh%20(they%2F%20he)%20teaches%20Constitutional%20Law%2C%20among%20other%20courses%2C%20at%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University.