%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Labour%20Party%20Chair%20Anneliese%20Dodds%20had%20said%20days%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FTA%20also%20featured%20prominently%20in%20the%20party's%20poll%20manifesto%20which%20stated%20their%20%26quot%3Bcommitment%20to%20pursue%20a%20new%20strategic%20partnership%26quot%3B%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarmer%20has%20pledged%20to%20forge%20a%20new%20strategic%20partnership%20with%20India%20and%20enhanced%20bilateral%20cooperation%20in%20technology%2C%20security%2C%20education%2C%20and%20climate%20change%20underscores%20his%20ambition%20to%20elevate%20relations%20with%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20fastest-growing%20economies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20UK's%20insistence%20on%20lowering%20tariffs%2C%20which%20can%20be%20as%20high%20as%20150%25%20on%20key%20exports%20like%20food%20and%20automobiles%2C%20remains%20a%20sticking%20point%20in%20the%20trade%20deal%20talks.%20Additionally%2C%20issues%20regarding%20the%20UK's%20immigration%20policies%2C%20particularly%20concerning%20Indian%20service%20sector%20workers%2C%20continue%20to%20challenge%20the%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20India%20has%20raised%20concerns%20about%20proposed%20UK%20regulations%2C%20such%20as%20the%20carbon%20tax%20akin%20to%20the%20EU's%20carbon%20border%20adjustment%20mechanism%2C%20which%20could%20potentially%20undermine%20the%20tariff%20concessions%20agreed%20upon%20in%20the%20FTA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20virtual%20meetings%20between%20Indian%20and%20UK%20officials%20in%20May%20aimed%20to%20restart%20discussions%2C%20focusing%20on%20economic%20assessments%20and%20the%20inclusion%20of%20new%20disciplines%20like%20environment%2C%20labour%2C%20gender%20issues%2C%20and%20digital%20trade%20in%20the%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20currently%20engaged%20in%20FTA%20negotiations%20with%20several%20other%20nations%20and%20unions%20including%20the%20EU%2C%20Australia%2C%20Eurasian%20Economic%20Union%2C