2Frest-of-world%2Fworld-food-prices-hold-firm-in-june-uns-fao-reports%2Farticleshow%2F111510759.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fworld-food-prices-hold-firm-in-june-uns-fao-reports%2Famp_articleshow%2F111510759.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fworld-food-prices-hold-firm-in-june-uns-fao-reports%2Famp_articleshow%2F111510759.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20NEET%20PG%20Exam%20Dates%20Announced%202%20Weeks%20After%20They%20Were%20Postponed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Board%20of%20Examinations%20(NBE)%20on%20Friday%20announced%20the%20date%20for%20NEET-PG%20exam%2C%20which%20is%20held%20for%20admission%20to%20postgraduate%20medical%20courses.%20The%20agency%20has%20set%20August%2011%20as%20the%20date%20of%20examination.%20It%20will%20be%20held%20in%20two%20shifts%2C%20a%20release%20from%20the%20agency%20said.%20Scheduled%20for%20June%2022%2C%20the%20NEET-PG%20exam%20was%20postponed%20hours%20before%20its%20start%20amid%20a%20row%20over%20alleged%20irregularities%2C%20including%20leaked%20papers%2C%20for%20the%20UG%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20exam%2C%20NBE%20president%20Dr%20Abhijat%20Seth%20had%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20as%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20wanted%20to%20check%20the%20robustness%20of%20the%20exam%20process%20and%20get%20the%20assurance%20that%20there%20is%20no%20vulnerability%20in%20this%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NBE%20has%20been%20conducting%20NEET-PG%20for%20the%20past%20seven%20years%20and%20there%20have%20not%20been%20any%20report%20of%20a%20paper%20leak%20owing%20to%20the%20board's%20stringent%20SOPs%2C%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20of%20new%20date%20comes%20days%20after%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20officials%20met%20the%20government's%20anti-cybercrime%20body%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20exam%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20had%20said%20that%20it%20would%20carry%20out%20a%20thorough%20assessment%20of%20the%20robustness%20of%20the%20process%20of%20NEET-PG.%20Among%20the%20measures%20suggested%20at%20the%20meeting%20were%20preparing%20the%20question%20paper%20two%20hours%20before%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENEET-PG%20is%20held%20to%20assess%20the%20eligibility%20of%20MBBS%20degree%20holders%20for%20enrolment%20in%20postgraduate%20medical%20courses%20in%20government%20and%20private%20medical%20colleges%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20students%20launched%20protest%20across%20the%20country%20amid%20a%20massive%20row%20over%20the%20NEET-UG%20paper%20leak%20and%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20UGC-NET.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%2050%20successful%20Gujarat-based%20NEET-UG%20candidates%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20a%20direction%20to%20restrain%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%20from%20cancelling%20the%20controversy-ridden%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20was%20filed%20days%20before%20a%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20is%20scheduled%20to%20hear%20as%20many%20as%2026%20petitions%20seeking%20reliefs%20like%20re-test%20and%20probe%20into%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20examination%20plagued%20by%20allegations%20of%20malpractices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2067%20students%20had%20scored%20a%20perfect%20720%2C%20unprecedented%20in%20the%20NTA's%20history%2C%20with%20six%20from%20a%20Haryana%20centre%20figuring%20in%20the%20list%2C%20raising%20suspicions%20about%20irregularities%20in%20the%20examination%20held%20on%20May%205.%20It%20has%20been%20alleged%20that%20grace%20marks%20contributed%20to%2067%20students%20sharing%20the%20top%20rank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20candidates%20sharing%20the%20top%20rank%20in%20the%20NEET-UG%20came%20down%20to%2061%20from%2067%20in%20the%20revised%20results%20announced%20by%20the%20NTA.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720170480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F8kin8q6g_entrance-exam-generic_625x300_14_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fneet-pg-examination-on-august-11-it-was-postponed-last-month-6039373%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%20has%20set%20August%2011%20as%20the%20date%20of%20examination.%20It%20will%20be%20held%20in%20two%20shifts%2C%20a%20release%20from%20the%20agency%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fneet-pg-examination-on-august-11-it-was-postponed-last-month-6039373%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fneet-pg-examination-on-august-11-it-was-postponed-last-month-6039373%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fneet-pg-examination-on-august-11-it-was-postponed-last-month-6039373%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%20Man%20Bites%20Snake%20That%20Bit%20Him.%20Here's%20What%20Happened%20Next%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Bihar%20man%2C%20who%20was%20bitten%20by%20a%20snake%2C%20bit%20it%20back%2C%20killing%20the%20reptile.%20Santosh%20Lohar%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Navada%2C%20was%20sleeping%20at%20his%20base%20camp%20after%20a%20day's%20work%20on%20laying%20railway%20lines%20when%20the%20snake%20attacked%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDriven%20by%20a%20superstition%20that%20biting%20the%20snake%20back%20would%20neutralise%20its%20venom%2C%20the%2035-year-old%20took%20matters%20into%20his%20own%20hands%20and%20bit%20the%20snake%20twice.%20This%20unconventional%20response%20led%20to%20the%20snake's%20death%2C%20but%20it%20also%20landed%20Mr%20Lohar%20in%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20colleagues%20rushed%20him%20to%20the%20Rajauli%20subdivision%20hospital%20where%20he%20received%20treatment.%20Mr%20Lohar%20recovered%20fast%20and%C2%A0was%20discharged%20the%20next%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20a%20man%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Fatehpur%20miraculously%20survived%20five%20snake%20bites%20in%20nearly%20two%20months%2C%20leaving%20the%20doctors%20astonished.%20The%20bites%20occurred%20on%20June%202%2C%20June%2010%2C%20and%20June%2017%2C%20and%20twice%20in%20July.%20His%20condition%20is%20now%20stable%2C%20and%20the%20case%20has%20been%20deemed%20%26quot%3Bstrange%26quot%3B%20by%20medical%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20do%20after%20a%20snake%20bite%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20of%20a%20snake%20bite%2C%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fteams%2Fcontrol-of-neglected-tropical-diseases%2Fsnakebite-envenoming%2Ftreatment%5C%22%3EWHO%3C%2Fa%3E)%20recommends%20acting%20quickly%20and%20seeking%20medical%20help.%20Immediate%20medical%20attention%20prevents%20complications%20and%20reduces%20the%20risk%20of%20long-term%20disability%20or%20death.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20bitten%20by%20a%20snake%2C%20move%20away%20from%20the%20area%20and%20remove%20any%20tight%20clothing%20or%20jewellery.%20Immobilise%20the%20affected%20limb%20and%20keep%20it%20still.%20Do%20not%20attempt%20to%20suck%20out%20the%20venom.%20Instead%2C%20take%20the%20victim%20to%20a%20health%20facility%20quickly%20and%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20waiting%20for%20medical%20attention%2C%20provide%20basic%20first%20aid%20by%20keeping%20the%20affected%20limb%20below%20heart%20level.%20Do%20not%20give%20the%20victim%20anything%20to%20eat%20or%20drink%20and%20avoid%20applying%20ice%20or%20heat.%20If%20the%20snake%20is%20still%20attached%2C%20use%20a%20stick%20or%20tool%20to%20carefully%20remove%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720170420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2F2nb86q78_snake-generic_6