eakdown%20Of%20Perks%20And%20Benefits%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20elections%20in%20the%20UK%20saw%20Labour%20registering%20a%20landslide%20victory%20and%20ending%20the%20Tories'%2014-year%20grip%20on%20power.%20Keir%20Starmer%20will%20replace%20Rishi%20Sunak%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20after%20Labour%20won%20410%20of%20the%20650%20seats%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%2C%20the%20most%20since%20Tony%20Blair's%201997%20landslide.%20The%20election%20will%20reshape%20the%20political%20landscape%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20with%20task%20cut%20out%20for%20the%20incoming%20Prime%20Minister.%20But%20how%20much%20will%20Mr%20Starmer%20be%20paid%20for%20the%20epic%20job%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20UK%20Parliament%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20entitled%20to%20an%20annual%20salary%20of%20172%2C153%20pounds.%20His%20earnings%20are%20made%20up%20of%2080%2C807%20pounds%20for%20the%20role%20of%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20and%20an%20additional%2091%2C346%20pounds%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.parliament.uk%2Fabout%2Fmps-and-lords%2Fmembers%2Fpay-mps%2F%5C%22%3Erevised%20on%20April%201%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E)%20for%20being%20an%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20out%20of%20the%20total%20amount%2C%2075%2C440%20pounds%20is%20actually%20claimed.%20As%20per%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%20website%2C%20MPs%20pay%20the%20same%20tax%20and%20national%20insurance%20as%20any%20other%20employed%20person%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20of%20a%20PM%20has%20never%20been%20astronomically%20well-paid%20compared%20with%20other%20professions%20of%20similar%20responsibility.%20According%20to%20an%20old%20by%20%3Cem%3EBBC%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20previous%20prime%20ministers%20have%20previously%20found%20themselves%20drowning%20in%20debt%20and%20requiring%20a%20bail-out%20from%20the%20monarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fvoices%2Fuk-prime-minister-salary-rishi-sunak-b2342294.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Independent%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20significant%20fall%20in%20the%20standard%20of%20living%20for%20UK%20Prime%20Ministers%20over%20the%20centuries.%20In%20the%2018th%20century%2C%20William%20Pitt%20received%2010%2C500%20pounds%20per%20annum%20as%20first%20lord%20of%20the%20Treasury.%20The%20Marquess%20of%20Salisbury%2C%20incumbent%20PM%20at%20the%20turn%20of%20the%2020th%20century%2C%20was%20on%205%2C000%20pounds%20per%20annum%20-%20or%20a%20half%20a%20million%20pounds%20according%20today's%20exchange%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%201937%2C%20the%20prime%20minister's%20annual%20pay%20was%20the%20equivalent%20of%20a%20modern%20600%2C000%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Public%20Duty%20Costs%20Allowance%20(PDCA)%2C%20which%20was%20established%20following%20the%20resignation%20of%20Margaret%20Thatcher%2C%20allows%20former%20Prime%20Ministers%20to%20claim%20up%20to%20115%2C000%20pounds%20annually%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bnecessary%20office%20costs%20and%20secretarial%20costs%20arising%20from%20their%20special%20position%20in%20public%20life%26quot%3B.%20These%20costs%20can%20be%20claimed%20for%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720168980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F6m3vut5o_keir-starmer_625x300_05_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-much-does-a-uk-prime-minister-earn-a-breakdown-of-perks-and-benefits-6039341%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20job%20of%20a%20PM%20has%20never%20been%20astronomically%20well-paid%20compared%20with%20other%20professions%20of%20similar%20responsibility.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-much-does-a-uk-prime-minister-earn-a-breakdown-of-perks-and-benefits-6039341%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-much-does-a-uk-prime-ministe