rmful%20to%20the%20environment%20but%20also%20to%20human%20health.%20In%20cities%20like%20Delhi%2C%20you%20can%20see%20mountains%20of%20waste.%20While%20the%20Government%20spends%20crores%20on%20waste%20management%2C%20there%20is%20a%20public%20outcry%20around%20plastic%20pollution.%20We%20need%20an%20urgent%20solution%20to%20divert%20this%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20looking%20for%20alternatives%20for%20disposing%20of%20plastic%20waste%2C%20Dr%20Balamukund%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20use%20plastic%20waste%20by%20replacing%20reinforced%20concrete%20houses%20conventionally%20made%20of%20bricks%20and%20cement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-1-1720100210.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20house%20is%20currently%20being%20used%20by%20tourists%20and%20breastfeeding%20mothers%20visiting%20the%20garden.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-1-1720100210.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-1-1720100210-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-1-1720100210-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-1-1720100210-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-1-1720100210-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355660%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20house%20is%20currently%20being%20used%20by%20tourists%20and%20breastfeeding%20mothers%20visiting%20the%20garden.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20concrete%20has%20been%20putting%20roofs%20over%20the%20heads%20of%20billions.%20After%20water%2C%20concrete%20is%20the%20most%20widely%20used%20substance%20on%20Earth.%20Concrete%20is%20a%20thirsty%20behemoth%2C%20sucking%20up%20almost%20a%20tenth%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20industrial%20water%20use.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20cement%20industry%20were%20a%20country%2C%20it%20would%20be%20the%20third%20largest%20carbon%20dioxide%20emitter%20in%20the%20world%20with%20up%20to%202.8bn%20tonnes%2C%20surpassed%20only%20by%20China%20and%20the%20US%2C%E2%80%9D%20mentions%20a%20report%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fcities%2F2019%2Ffeb%2F25%2Fconcrete-the-most-destructive-material-on-earth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20also%20quoted%20concrete%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20most%20destructive%20material%20to%20Earth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Balmukund%20says%20he%20was%20inspired%20to%20tackle%20plastic%20waste%20in%202014%20when%20the%20Swachhata%20Bharat%20Abhiyan%20was%20launched.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20also%20inspired%20by%20my%20mother.%20Back%20in%20the%2060s%2C%20she%20used%20to%20wear%20polyester%20sarees.%20She%20would%20burn%20worn-out%20sarees.%20When%20polyester%20burns%2C%20it%20gives%20a%20plasticy%20smell%20and%20the%20fabric%20melts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20would%20mix%20the%20molten%20fabric%20with%20ash%20from%20%3Cem%3Echulha%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20make%20a%20thick%20paste.%20She%20would%20apply%20the%20semi-solid%20substance%20onto%20a%20bamboo%20%3Cem%3Esoop%3C%2Fem%3E%20(traditional%20tray)%20to%20make%20it%20rigid.%20This%20would%20increase%20its%20durability%20from%20a%20year%20to%20four%20years.%20Later%20on%2C%20she%20started%20using%20it%20to%20fix%20broken%20pans%20and%20drums.%20She%20never%20went%20to%20school%20but%20I%20learnt%20a%20lot%20from%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20a