ratures%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCompared%20to%20a%20cement%20home%2C%20you%20do%20not%20require%20any%20water%20to%20construct%20a%20plastic%20house.%20Also%2C%20in%20reinforced%20concrete%2C%20percolation%20and%20cracks%20will%20eventually%20occur%2C%20but%20in%20a%20plastic%20home%2C%20there%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20any%20cracks.%20The%20reinforced%20cemented%20structures%20require%20maintenance%20in%2020%20to%2025%20years%20but%20no%20such%20maintenance%20is%20needed%20in%20structures%20made%20of%20plastic%2C%20which%20can%20last%20for%20decades%2C%20even%20after%20your%20lifetime%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-15-1720100001.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22How%20to%20build%20a%20plastic%20house%3F%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-15-1720100001.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-15-1720100001-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-15-1720100001-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-15-1720100001-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-15-1720100001-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355657%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20safety%20risks%2C%20Dr%20Balmukund%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20house%20is%20rust-free%2C%20fireproof%2C%20and%20shock-free.%20Usually%2C%20plastic%20melts%20at%20around%20250%20degrees%20and%20requires%20above%20300%20degrees%20for%20it%20to%20burn.%20Wooden%20homes%20catch%20fire%20faster%20than%20a%20plastic%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChandrapur%20city%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20polluted%20cities%20as%20it%20is%20an%20industrial%20area%20with%20mines%2C%20cement%20and%20explosives%20factories.%20We%20stressed%20on%20ways%20to%20reduce%20pollution.%20Dr%20Paliwal%20pitched%20in%20to%20design%20a%20house%20made%20of%20plastic.%20Although%20I%20was%20very%20doubtful%2C%20he%20was%20very%20confident.%20Let%20alone%20the%20public%2C%20even%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20see%20the%20final%20house.%20When%20it%20was%20inaugurated%2C%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20could%20not%20believe%20their%20eyes%2C%E2%80%9D%20IAS%20Vivek%20Johnson%20tells%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20demo%20house%20which%20can%20be%20replicated%20in%20the%20housing%20scheme%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana.%20By%20constructing%20such%20homes%2C%20tonnes%20of%20plastic%20waste%20from%20villages%20and%20cities%20can%20be%20utilised.%20In%20future%2C%20if%20you%20ever%20desire%20to%20dismantle%20the%20house%2C%20you%20can%20reuse%20and%20recycle%20all%20the%20demolished%20plastic%20material%2C%20which%20is%20not%20possible%20in%20reinforced%20concrete%20structures.%20By%20adopting%20such%20a%20house%2C%20you%20protect%20the%20environment%2C%20use%20less%20natural%20resources%2C%20reduce%20plastic%20waste%2C%20and%20generate%20employment%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Balmukund.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncluding%20collection%2C%20machinery%2C%20and%20labour%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20constructing%20the%20plastic%20house%20was%20Rs%209%20lakh%2C%20claims%20the%20doctor.%20Of%20the%20total%20cost%2C%20the%20Zila%20Parishad%20sanctioned%20Rs%205%20lakh%20(the%20upper%20limit%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20demo%20house).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20comparatively%2020%20percent%20less%20than%20the%20conventional%20cemented%20house.%20I%20invested%20the%20remaining%20amount%20so%20that%20funds%20do%20not%20become%20an%20issue%20and%20we%20have%20an%20example%20for%20others%20to%20adopt.%20As%20citizens%2C%20we%20need%20to%20understand%20our%20responsibilities%20towards%20protecting%20the%20environment.%20I%20am%20doing%20my%20bit%2C%20and%20I%20seek%20public%20and%20Government%20support%20to%20promote%20such%20houses%20to%20benefit%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Dr%20Balmukund%20Paliwal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720102772000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fplastic-house-2-1720100452.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D355647%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Balmukund%20Paliwal%20built%20a%20two-storey%20house%20in%20Chandrapur%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20using%20recycled%20plastic%20waste%20and%20preventing%2013%20tonnes%20of%20plastic%20from%20reaching%20landfills.%20Here's%20how%20he%20did%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355647%2Fdr-balmukund-paliwal-builds-plastic-house-chandrapur-maharashtra-recycled-waste-cement-free%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%26nbsp%3BBest%26nbsp%3BFarm-To-Table%20Dining%20Experiences%20You%20Must%20Try%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPicture%20this%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20The%20table%20in%20front%20of%20you%20is%20set%20with%20crockery%20and%20cutlery.%20If%20they%20could%20converse%2C%20they%20would%20tell%20you%20that%20you%E2%80%99re%20in%20for%20a%20feast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20is%20resplendent%20with%20a%20bounty%20of%20sounds%20%E2%80%94%20the%20crackle%20of%20something%20delicious%20being%20fried%2C%20the%20gentle%20bubbling%20of%20a%20soup%2