2_blank%5C%22%3ECEE%3C%2Fa%3E)%20mentions%20that%20India%20is%20the%20fifth%20largest%20broiler%20meat-producing%20country%20after%20the%20USA%2C%20European%20Union%2C%20Brazil%2C%20and%20China%2C%20with%20over%204.6%20million%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20annual%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupported%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%2C%20CEE%20is%20a%20national%20institute%20dedicated%20to%20enhancing%20public%20awareness%20about%20the%20environment.%20It%20also%20states%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpoultry%20waste%20needs%20urgent%20attention%20as%20a%20formal%20management%20does%20not%20exist%20for%20this%20waste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20estimated%20that%20the%20generation%20of%20poultry%20waste%20is%20approximately%2020%20tonnes%20per%20day%2C%20just%20within%20the%20city%20of%20Ahmedabad.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20%5Bpoultry%20waste%5D%20is%20either%20sold%20to%20middlemen%20(for%20processing%20some%20body%20parts%20into%20fish%20feed%2C%20manure%20etc)%20or%20disposed%20of%20in%20municipal%20dumping%20sites%20without%20any%20treatment%2C%20which%20is%20against%20the%20law%20and%20is%20causing%20issues%20related%20to%20environmental%20pollution%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-3-1718797680.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Radhesh%20is%20able%20to%20make%20natural%20wool-like%20fibre%20similar%20to%20cotton%2C%20jute%2C%20wool%2C%20and%20silk.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-3-1718797680.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-3-1718797680-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-3-1718797680-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-3-1718797680-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-3-1718797680-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353388%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERadhesh%20can%20make%20natural%20wool-like%20fibre%20similar%20to%20cotton%2C%20jute%2C%20wool%2C%20and%20silk.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERadhesh%20remarks%20that%20in%20a%20country%20where%20rivers%20are%20worshipped%20as%20mothers%2C%20the%20butchery%20waste%20comprising%20intestines%2C%20blood%2C%20skin%2C%20inner%20cells%2C%20and%20feathers%2C%20ends%20up%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F297496%2Framon-magsaysay-award-winner-gary-bencheghib-cleans-plastic-from-bali-indonesia-beaches%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epolluting%20river%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20also%20spreads%20communicable%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWaste%20from%20big%20bovine%20animals%20is%20used%20to%20make%20leather%2C%20pet%20foods%2C%20and%20more%2C%20whereas%20chicken%20butchery%20waste%20is%20either%20incinerated%20or%20ends%20up%20in%20landfills%20and%20water%20bodies.%20The%20incineration%20process%20releases%20huge%20amounts%20of%20carbon%20emissions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20the%20entire%20world%20is%20working%20towards%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F319912%2Ftamil-nadu-father-son-duo-senthil-kumar-recycle-plastic-bottles-into-sustainable-clothes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20recycling%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20not%20many%20are%20talking%20about%20chicken%20butchery%20waste.%20However%2C%20instead%20of%20making%20slogans%20to%20clean%20water%20bodies%2C%20we%20really%20need%20to%20work%20on%20grassroots%20to%20solve%20the%20root%20causes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20shawls%2C%20quilts%2C%20and%20paper%20from%20chicken%20waste%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20do%20his%20bit%2C%20Radhesh%20launched%20his%20company%20in%202019.%20Explaining%20its%20functioning%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20we%20collect%20waste%20from%20slaughterhouses%20and%20then%20we%20sterilise%20and%20sanitise%20it%20in%20a%20hygienic%20way%20using%20100%20degrees%20steam%20process%20to%20kill%20the%20various%20worms%20present%20in%20the%20waste.%20Using%20our%20patented%20technology%2C%20we%20use%20natural%20ingredients%20to%20process%20the%20waste%20into%20wool-like%20fibre%20which%20is%20similar%20to%20pashmina%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChicken%20is%20a%20fowl%20and%20it%20has%20feathers%20similar%20to%20other%20birds.%20Feathers%20themselves%20are%20lightweight%20and%20using%20that%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20make%20natural%20wool-like%20fibre%20similar%20to%20cotton%2C%20jute%2C%20wool%2C%20and%20silk.%20This%20woollen%20fibre%20is%20soft%2C%20warm%20and%20durable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20purpose%2C%20Radhesh%20says%20he%20has%20trained%201%2C200%20tribal%20women%20of%20Rajasthan%20who%20weave%20and%20spin%20the%20waste%20into%20fibre.%20Feathers%20which%20are%20not%20good%20for%20spinning%20are%20used%20to%20make%20handmade%20paper%20or%20converted%20into%20fillers%20for%20quilts%2C%20jackets%2C%20and%20pillows.%20In%20this%20process%2C%20the%20byproduct%20of%20chicken%20butchery%20waste%20is%20converted%20into%20compost%20and%20fish%20feed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-1718797164.jpg%